<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="glass-n">glass <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡlɑːs/    美 /ɡlæs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>玻璃；[总称] 玻璃制品：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Glass breaks easily.
玻璃易碎。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>玻璃杯；一杯 (的容量)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'll get you <strong>a glass of</strong> water.
我给你倒杯水。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[复数] 眼镜：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>pair of glasses</strong>
一副眼镜</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I must put on my glasses to read this letter.
我必须戴上眼镜读这封信。</p></div></div>